description: Theta series of 18-dimensional lattice associated with Sp_4(4), with det 256 and minimal norm 3.
references: N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
extensions: In the Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences this lattice was incorrectly described as the laminated lattice LAMBDA_18.
